Summary Table
Direction	Library/Service	Code Style	Secure?
Outbound (send)	Twilio, Vonage	SDK/API call	Yes, if using HTTPS and env vars
Inbound (recv)	Twilio, Vonage	Express webhook	Yes, if HTTPS and signature validation
